# UNJYNX UI/UX MASTER IDEAS DOCUMENT
# Generated: 2026-03-10 | Sources: 50+ research articles, competitive analysis, UI/UX Pro Max tool
# Covers: All 66 screens + design system + 12 original innovations + implementation priorities


========================================================================
PART 1: DESIGN SYSTEM UPGRADES (Beyond Current Spec)
========================================================================

## 1.1 GLASSMORPHISM CARD SYSTEM (#1 Visual Upgrade)

Apple Liquid Glass (iOS 26, WWDC June 2025) made glassmorphism THE defining UI of 2026. 64% of premium apps use it. 23% higher perceived quality. Midnight purple + frosted glass = PERFECT.

Dark mode: ClipRRect + BackdropFilter(blur:12px) + white 8% fill + 1px rgba(208,188,255,0.15) border
Light mode: ClipRRect + BackdropFilter(blur:8px) + white 60% fill + 1px rgba(107,33,168,0.08) border
Hero cards (Rings, Content) get purple-to-gold gradient border that shimmers on interaction.
3 glass depth levels: surface glass, elevated glass, modal glass (increasing blur/opacity).

Flutter pattern:
  ClipRRect(borderRadius: 16, child: BackdropFilter(
    filter: ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX:12, sigmaY:12),
    child: Container(decoration: BoxDecoration(
      color: Colors.white.withOpacity(isDark ? 0.08 : 0.6),
      border: Border.all(color: violet.withOpacity(isDark ? 0.15 : 0.08))
    ))
  ))

WHY: Todoist=flat. TickTick=basic Material. UNJYNX glassmorphism on midnight purple = nothing else exists.


## 1.2 LIVING GRADIENT BACKGROUND

Background = slowly-animating gradient mesh, 3-4 points drifting over 60s (Perlin noise).
PRODUCTIVE (3+ done): #0F0A1A->#1A0533->#2D1B69 + sparse gold particles
IDLE: muted #0F0A1A->#1A0533, no particles
ALL DONE: warm gold wash + 20-30 golden shimmer particles (slow drift)
OVERDUE: very subtle warm/red tint in one gradient point
Performance: Single CustomPainter+RepaintBoundary, GPU-optimized. Fragment Shader where supported.
prefers-reduced-motion: static gradient.


## 1.3 RIVE INTERACTIVE ANIMATIONS (Replace Lottie for Key Elements)

Rive = 3.5x framerate of Lottie, 15x smaller files. Duolingo switched.
USE RIVE (interactive, state-driven): Progress Rings, Streak flame, Checkbox, Pomodoro ring, XP bar, Ghost Mode breathing, Splash logo, Tab bar icons
USE LOTTIE (fire-and-forget): Confetti, Achievement unlocks, Empty states, Seasonal, Skeletons
Key advantage: Rive animations RESPOND to data. Ring grows with completion. Flame evolves with streak.


## 1.4 HAPTIC LANGUAGE SYSTEM (Original Innovation)

No productivity app has systematic haptics. UNJYNX owns this.
COMPLETION: single=medium tap, last=success(light-medium-heavy), ring=double+sustained, streak=ascending
NAVIGATION: tab=light tick, sheet=soft thud, pull-refresh=selection click
ALERT: overdue=gentle double buzz, timer=rhythmic triple tap
GHOST MODE: all haptics 50% intensity. Settings: Off/Subtle/Standard/Strong.


========================================================================
PART 2: SCREEN-BY-SCREEN ENHANCEMENT IDEAS
========================================================================

== A. PRE-AUTH (A1-A3) ==

A1. SPLASH - "Curse-Breaking Reveal"
- PARTICLE GENESIS: Black -> single gold particle -> splits into thousands forming logotype. Rive state machine (genesis->forming->solid). 1.5s.
- DARK-TO-DARK CONTINUITY: Logo particles SCATTER outward, Home elements fade in from particle positions. Splash BECOMES the app.
- RETURNING USER: After week 1, 0.8s. Logo appears formed, brief gold pulse.

A2. LOGIN - "The Gateway"
- PARALLAX DEPTH: 3 layers behind glass card. Far: purple nebula. Mid: gold constellation. Near: glass login card. Accelerometer.
- GLASS SOCIAL BUTTONS: Each = glass card + provider icon. Press = glow in brand color. Stagger-in 50ms.
- ANIMATED TAGLINE: "Break the Satisfactory" letter-by-letter (30ms/letter). Gold underline draws after.
- BIOMETRIC (returning): fingerprint/face + "Welcome back, [Name]" -> single tap -> Home.


== B. ONBOARDING (B1-B4) ==

B1. CAROUSEL - "The Hook" (77% abandon in 3 days)
- INTERACTIVE SLIDE 1: 5 scattered task bubbles. User TAPS each -> snaps to list. Last = chain-breaking. User PARTICIPATED.
- INTERACTIVE SLIDE 2: Phone mockup, channel icons orbit. Swipe = real notification preview per channel.
- INTERACTIVE SLIDE 3: Split screen chaos->order. Drag slider to morph. Ghost Mode at max.
- PROGRESS = CHAIN BREAKING: 3 chain links break per slide. Snap + haptic. All broken -> "Let's Unjynx!"

B2. PERSONALIZATION
- IDENTITY: Glass cards + Rive-animated icons. Tap=elevate+celebrate. Others dim.
- GOALS: Chips drift in as cloud. Selected rise + glow gold, group magnetically. Metaphor: goals rise above noise.
- CHANNELS: Toggle ON -> animated preview of ACTUAL channel notification. Value tangible before setup.
- CONTENT: Swipeable full-screen cards (Tinder-style). Up=love, down=skip. Playfair quote. Bg shifts per category.

B3. FIRST TASK
- CONVERSATIONAL: Chat-like. "First curse to break?" -> user types -> "Buy milk tomorrow 9AM. Right?" -> "Yes!"
- FIRST COMPLETION: "Crush it now?" -> Done = FULL celebration. Chains break, dust, ring moves. "One down. Curse weakens." MOST IMPORTANT MOMENT.
- VOICE: Live gold waveform + real-time transcription.


== C. HOME SCREEN (C1) - "Command Center" ==

GREETING:
- Morning "break some curses" / Afternoon "[N] tasks left" / Evening "close those rings" / Late night "night owl energy" / Monday "fresh curses" / Friday "finish strong" / All done "go live your best life"
- Weather-aware (permission): Rainy="Perfect for indoor productivity"

STREAK FLAME (Rive):
- 1-6d: spark | 7-13: candle | 14-29: flame | 30-99: gold flame | 100-364: blue-gold | 365+: purple-gold legendary
- Flickers with scroll. Tap = streak detail glass card.

PROGRESS RINGS:
- URGENCY GRADIENT: 0-25% muted -> 75-99% full brightness+glow -> 100% gold pulse
- OVERACHIEVEMENT: Past 100% = second transparent lap. "120% Overachiever"
- WEEKLY SPARKLINE: 7-day trend (60x16px) below each ring. Green if improving.

DAILY CONTENT:
- PARALLAX CARD: 3 layers respond to device tilt. Feels PHYSICAL.
- SHARE AS STORY: 1-tap 9:16 image. 5 styles (Classic/Minimal/Bold/Artistic/Dark). UNJYNX watermark. #1 ORGANIC GROWTH.
- QUOTE TRANSITION: Fades left, new materializes letter-by-letter (300ms).

TASKS:
- PRIORITY GLOW: P1=gold edge glow(2px). P2=amber. P3/P4=none. Natural hierarchy.
- ENERGY-ADAPTIVE ORDER: Morning=high-energy top, afternoon=medium, evening=low.
- SWIPE: RIGHT=green+spring. LEFT=3 icons. Rubber-band resistance.

QUICK ACTIONS: Glass pill buttons (icon+label). Active fills with accent.
AI INSIGHT: "UNJYNX WHISPERS" + crystal ball icon. Magical, not technical.


== D. TASK MANAGEMENT (D1-D6) ==

D1. QUICK CREATE:
- NLP LIVE PREVIEW: Parsed chips below text in real-time. [Buy milk] [Mar 11] [9 AM]. Color-coded. Tap to override.
- ADD ANOTHER: After create, text clears, cursor ready. Rapid-fire without reopening.

D2. TASK DETAIL:
- HERO TRANSITION: Card EXPANDS to full screen. Shared element: bg expands, title morphs, project dot -> header bar.
- INLINE EDITING: Every field tappable inline. No edit mode. Auto-save. Linear-style.
- SUBTASK SEGMENTS: Visual bar (not "3/5"). Each segment fills with spring on completion.

D3. TASK LIST:
- FILTER ANIMATION: Items stagger out/in (30ms each). Matching fade IN from below.
- SMART HEADERS: "Today - 3 left, halfway!" not "Today (6)".

D4. KANBAN:
- DRAG PHYSICS: Elevate+shadow, source/target gaps spring, drop overshoots. Headers glow.
- WIP LIMIT: Color dots. Column rejects with shake when over limit.

D5. RECURRING:
- VISUAL PREVIEW: Mini calendar, next 5 occurrences as gold dots. Animate on change.

D6. TEMPLATES:
- CARDS: Mini task tree viz. "Used 1,247 times" social proof. "4.8/5" rating.


== E. PROJECTS (E1-E4) ==

E1. LIST:
- GLASS CARDS: Project color gradient left edge. Gold progress line bottom. Avatar stacks.
- FAVORITES CAROUSEL: Horizontal scroll above list. Large cards. ONE-tap access.

E2. DETAIL:
- HEALTH: Green/amber/red heartbeat. >=80%=green, <50%=red.
- VIEW TOGGLE: List->Kanban: cards FLY between positions. 400ms staggered.


== F. CALENDAR (F1-F3) ==

F1. CALENDAR:
- HEATMAP MONTH: Cells tinted by density (0=none, 1-2=subtle purple, 3-5=medium, 6+=deep+gold).
- DRAG RESCHEDULE: Long press -> tasks peek as pills. Drag to another day.
- GOLD TIME LINE: Current time = gold horizontal line, moving live.

F2. TIME BLOCKING:
- SPLIT-SCREEN: Left inbox (draggable), right timeline. Empty slots GLOW. Snap 15min+haptic.
- AUTO-SCHEDULE: Tasks fly inbox->timeline (staggered). Semi-transparent until confirmed.

F3. POMODORO - "Focus Forge":
- AMBIENT PARTICLES: Rain=blue drops, Forest=green leaves, Cafe=warm orange, Lo-fi=purple notes. 5-10 particles, 30% opacity.
- TIMER: 12dp gold ring. Bebas Neue 48sp. Task title below. Session counter.
- BUBBLE: Navigate away = draggable mini-ring + time.
- BREAK: Lighter purple, emerald ring. "Breathe. You earned this." Breathing circle (4-4-4).


== G. GHOST MODE - "The Sanctuary" ==

- PARTICLES: 20-30 purple, 10-15% opacity, floating up. Parallax on device movement.
- BREATHING GUIDE: Optional ring (4s expand/hold/contract). Purple+gold edge.
- COMPLETION: Task dissolves to gold particles -> drift up -> 2s pause -> next materializes.
- ZEN ALL DONE: Particles converge -> lotus outline -> glow gold. "Peace. You conquered today."


== H. CONTENT & RITUALS (H1-H4) ==

H1. CONTENT FEED:
- FULL-SCREEN: Unique gradient per category (Stoic=charcoal, Indian=amber, Humor=black, Anime=blue, all ->purple). Playfair gold.
- SHARE: 5 styles. Watermark. FREE MARKETING per share.
- SAVE: Heart purple->gold gradient + particles. "Wisdom library" masonry grid.

H2. CATEGORIES:
- TALL CARDS (140x200dp): Rive icons + tagline + quote peek. Horizontal snap. Active=gold glow.

H3. MORNING RITUAL - "Dawn Protocol":
- SUNRISE BG: Step 1=night -> Step 2=pre-dawn blue -> Step 3=dawn pink -> Step 4=sunrise -> Step 5=gold wash -> Step 6=burst.
- MOOD SLIDER: Continuous gradient. Rive face morphs tired->energized as thumb moves.
- GRATITUDE: Each word glows gold briefly. Submit = text floats up and fades.

H4. EVENING REVIEW - "Twilight Debrief":
- MOONRISE: Bg dims through steps. Final=midnight blue+stars.
- RING REPLAY: Refill 0->final (2s staggered). Satisfying.
- CARRY FORWARD: Drag RIGHT=tomorrow (flies right). Drag LEFT=drop (crumbles). No shame.


== I. PROGRESS (I1-I4) ==

I1. HUB:
- HEATMAP: 52-week grid. 0=dark, 1-2=light purple, 3-5=violet, 6-9=bright, 10+=GOLD. "Year in Review" timelapse (3s). MOST MOTIVATING.
- STREAK EVOLUTION: spark->candle->campfire->bonfire->phoenix. Unique Rive per tier.
- BESTS: Glass trophy cards. Bebas Neue value. Crown for biggest. Horizontal scroll.

I2. DASHBOARD (Pro):
- LINEAR CHARTS: Gold line on purple, gradient fill. Draw-in animations.
- POLAR: 24 hour-segments from center. Peaks JUMP OUT. Better than any competitor.
- SANKEY: Created->(Deferred xN)->Completed/Dropped. "62% first try."

I4. GAME MODE:
- XP BAR: 4dp gold bar, fill pulses on gain. "Lv.8" Bebas Neue.
- BADGES: 80x100dp glass cards. Earned=shimmer. Unearned=silhouette+"?". Tap=flip.
- LEVELS: 1-5 "Getting Started", 6-10 "Momentum", 11-20 "In the Zone", 21-30 "Curse Breaker", 31-50 "Unjynxed", 50+ "Legendary".


== J. CHANNELS (J1-J6) ==

J1. HUB:
- LIVE STATUS: Green pulse=working, amber=issue, gray=disconnected.
- FALLBACK CHAIN: Visual [WhatsApp]->[Telegram]->[Email]->[Push]. Drag to reorder.
- USAGE: Per-channel quota bars. "7/10 WhatsApp today."

J2-J6: UNIFIED ANIMATION: Icon pulses->connects->tests->confetti in channel brand color.


== L. PROFILE ==

- AVATAR RING: Free=purple. Pro=gold shimmer. Team=dual-tone.
- COUNTERS: Animate 0->actual (1.5s ease-out). Bebas Neue.
- HEATMAP HERO: Full-width heatmap IS the profile.


== M. SETTINGS ==

- GLASS GROUPS: Each section = glass card + colored left border.
- LIVE PREVIEW: Theme toggle shows mini phone mockup. Font slider resizes live.
- SOUNDS: Grid, tap=plays. "Crystal Ding", "Zen Bell", "Cash Register".
- PLAN: Two glass cards (Free muted, Pro gold border). Lock icons glow.


========================================================================
PART 3: ORIGINAL UNJYNX-ONLY INNOVATIONS (Nobody Else Has These)
========================================================================

3.1 "CURSED" TASK VISUALIZATION
Tasks deferred 3+ times get dark purple AURA. Intensifies per deferral (3x=faint, 5x=noticeable, 7+=strong). Completing = aura SHATTERS, gold particles scatter. +10 XP in Game Mode. Loss aversion is 2x stronger than gain.

3.2 "ENERGY FLOW ENGINE"
Home card: predicted energy curve (smooth wave, 24h). Peak=gold, current=dot. "Peak: 9-11 AM." Tasks reorder by energy match. v1=rules, v2=ML.

3.3 "UNJYNX AURA" - Dynamic App Icon (iOS)
Icon CHANGES by streak. No streak=default. 7d=gold ring. 30d=+flame. 100d=gold tint. 365d=legendary. Users keep streaks for the icon. Social proof visible to everyone.

3.4 "PRODUCTIVITY WEATHER"
"Sunny (8 tasks)" / "Stormy (12 tasks, 3 deadlines)" / "Partly cloudy (1 deadline 3pm)". Weather icon. Instant complexity communication.

3.5 "CURSE BREAKING CHAIN" - Weekly Story
Sunday: scrollable story cards (IG format). "23 curses broken. Biggest: Quarterly Report - deferred twice, crushed Thursday." Shareable.

3.6 "PHANTOM TASKS" - Ghost Mode Easter Egg
Complete ALL in Ghost Mode -> 5s wait -> ghostly card: "Reward yourself." ("Walk"/"Snack"/"Text someone"). Special badge. Simple, memorable, shareable.

3.7 "THE UNJYNX EFFECT" - Before/After
30 days: split screen chaos->order. "In 30 days: [N] tasks, [X]-day streak, [Y] channels." Show at 30/90/365. RETENTION SUPERWEAPON.

3.8 "NOTIFICATION PERSONALITY"
Tone adapts per channel. WhatsApp=casual+emoji. Telegram=clean+buttons. SMS=compact. Email=professional. Just FEELS right on each.

3.9 WALLPAPER GENERATOR
10 templates: gradient mesh, constellation, logo, today quote, rings (real data), heatmap (real year), flame, minimalist, geometric, custom. Phone-res PNG. YOUR PHONE = UNJYNX BILLBOARD.

3.10 "TASK FUNERAL"
Permanently drop a task: card crumbles to golden dust, drifts away. Tiny "R.I.P." for 500ms. Funny, removes guilt, makes dropping feel like a CHOICE.

3.11 "CONSTELLATION MODE"
Alternative progress view: completed tasks as STARS in night sky. Tasks form constellations by project. "847 stars built." Unique, shareable.

3.12 "INBOX ZERO" CELEBRATION
Empty task list: rings briefly turn confetti, sky shimmers. "Zero tasks. Infinite possibility." Fades to calm empty state. Once per day.


